Output assets/flashcard.gif

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Padding 30

Hide
Type "./target/release/examples/flashcard"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Sleep 1000ms
Type "f"
Sleep 1300ms
Type "n"
Sleep 1000ms
Type "f"
Sleep 1300ms
Type "n"
Sleep 1000ms
Type "f"
Sleep 1500ms
Hide
Type "q"
